Class SpecialRoom

java.lang.Object
  entities.Room
      entities.SpecialRoom

public class SpecialRoom
extends Room

The class SpecialRoom is a child class of the Class Room in thr adventure game 'Go Sunset'. Its function is to be used when the player enters a 'Special Room'. The differences are that this Class includes the informations for Riddles, which are used when the player enters a Special Room.

Version:
2014.03.09
Author:
Louis Capitanchik, Joshua Mulcock, Alice Charterton, John Stones
